{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0011", "text": "這面告別 長崎市 那面到達 紐西蘭", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 2, 0, 3, 5, 5, 2, 4, 2, 9, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ze5", "min6", "gou3", "bit6", "coeng4", "kei1", "si5", "naa5", "min6", "dou3", "daat6", "nau2", "sai1", "laan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "面", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "告別", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "長崎市", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那面", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到達", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "紐西蘭", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "隨意門", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_253", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0012", "text": "要是這樣 行情緊湊 每日上街 亦成負擔", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 2, 0, 0, 9, 4, 5, 2, 3, 2, 0, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jiu3", "si6", "ze5", "joeng6", "hang4", "cing4", "gan2", "cau3", "mui5", "jat6", "gaai1", "jik6", "sing4", "fu6", "daam1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "要是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "行情", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "緊湊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "每日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上街", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "成", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "負擔", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "隨意門", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_253", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0013", "text": "一旦任性走開 我怕沒有路回來", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 2, 4, 9, 3, 5, 4, 2, 5, 2, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jat1", "daan3", "jam6", "sing3", "zau2", "hoi1", "ngo5", "paa3", "mut6", "jau5", "lou6", "wui4", "loi4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "一旦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "任性", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "走開", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "路", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "回來", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "隨意門", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_253", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0014", "text": "不要話我不該 我已習慣這四面牆", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 2, 5, 3, 3, 5, 5, 2, 4, 5, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "jiu3", "waa6", "ngo5", "bat1", "goi1", "ngo5", "ji5", "zaap6", "gwaan3", "ze5", "sei3", "min6", "coeng4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "話", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不該", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "習慣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "四面", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "牆", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "隨意門", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_253", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUz_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
